{{Nakshatras}}
'''Anuradha''' is the seventeenth [[nakshatra]] ([[lunar mansion]]) in [[Hindu astrology]] having a spread from 3°20' to 16°40'. Anuradha is ruled by Shani (Saturn). Mitra is the deity for Anuradha Nakshatra. [[Category:Hindu astrology]] [[Category:Nakshatra]] [[Category:Hindu astronomy]]
